channel.title: How to make my self a member on MY server?
channel.description: How do I make my self a member on my server lol? I tried to go into char files, picked mine and changed char is rights = 0 to 1. then when i loged in it said member schedin but i couldnt do member things. how do i fix this? also whats the command to make others members? isnt it like ::makemember<char name here>?

item.title: How to make my self a member on MY server?
item.dc:creator: @Pj_owns Pj owns
item.description:
@Pj_owns wrote:

Ok look its ::makemem(name) no space. And if your not online, you can just go to “data” and click on members, add your name there. Btw, make sure whoever you are making a member logs off before you do it, or it wont work. Hope that helped.
